	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I agree, which is why I've set up a <a href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/Placeholder_graphics" class="postlink">page on the wiki for users to contribute tile sheets</a>.<br /><br />But coding an engine from scratch will take a while. I've been considering doing so, but real life and more interesting one-off NES projects have always interfered.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


